ef=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/transitionend_event\"><code>transitionend</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/transitionrun_event\"><code>transitionrun</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/transitionstart_event\"><code>transitionstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/webkitmouseforcechanged_event\"><code>webkitmouseforcechanged</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/webkitmouseforcedown_event\"><code>webkitmouseforcedown</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/webkitmouseforceup_event\"><code>webkitmouseforceup</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/webkitmouseforcewillbegin_event\"><code>webkitmouseforcewillbegin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/wheel_event\"><code>wheel</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ec.9a.94.ec.95.bd","title":"요약","isH3":true,"content":"<p>주어진 요소의 속성 모음(collection)을 반환합니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ea.b5.ac.eb.ac.b8","title":"구문","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">var<i>attrs</i> =<i>element</i>.attributes;\n</pre>\n<p>반환하는 개체는 <code>Attr</code> 노드를 포함하는 <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Core/core.html#ID-1780488922\" rel=\" noopener\">NamedNodeMap</a> 형입니다. 요소가 지정된 속성이 없으면, 반환하는 개체는 길이가 0입니다. 이 속성은 읽기 전용입니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ec.98.88","title":"예","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">// 문서에서 첫 &lt;p&gt; 요소 얻기\nvar para = document.getElementsByTagName(\"p\")[0];\nvar atts = para.attributes;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ec.a3.bc.ec.9d.98","title":"주의","isH3":true,"content":"<p>모음의 항목은 이름과 찾아보기(index)로 접근할 수 있습니다. <code>NodeList</code>와는 달리, <code>NamedNodeMap</code>은 항목을 어떤 특정 순서로 유지하지 않음을 주의하세요.</p>\n<p>여러분은 문서에서 \"p1\" 요소의 모든 속성값을 찍는 다음 예에서처럼 요소의 속성을 열거(enumerate)할 때 오직 찾아보기로 접근(access by index)을 써야 합니다.</p>\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01//EN\"\n\"http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/strict.dtd\"&gt;\n\n&lt;html&gt;\n\n &lt;head&gt;\n  &lt;title&gt;Attributes example&lt;/title&gt;\n  &lt;script type=\"text/javascript\"&gt;\n   function showFirstAttr()\n   {\n    var firstPara = document.getElementById(\"p1\");\n    var outputText = document.getElementById(\"result\");\n\n    // 먼저, paragraph에 어떤 속성이 있는지 검증\n    if (firstPara.hasAttributes())\n    {\n      var attrs = firstPara.attributes;\n      var text = \"\";\n      for(var i=attrs.length-1; i&gt;=0; i--) {\n        text += attrs[i].name + \"-&gt;\" + attrs[i].value;\n      }\n      outputText.value = text;\n    } else {\n      outputText.value = \"No attributes to show\"\n    };\n   }\n  &lt;/script&gt;\n &lt;/head&gt;\n\n&lt;body&gt;\n &lt;p id=\"p1\" style=\"color: green;\"&gt;Sample Paragraph&lt;/p&gt;\n &lt;form action=\"\"&gt;\n  &lt;p&gt;&lt;input type=\"button\" value=\"Show first attribute name and value\"\n      onclick=\"showFirstAttr();\"&gt;\n  &lt;input id=\"result\" type=\"text\" value=\"\"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n &lt;/form&gt;\n&lt;/body&gt;\n&lt;/html&gt;\n</pre>\n<p><code>NamedNodeMap</code>은 배열처럼 반복될 수 있지만, <code>join</code>, <code>split</code> 등과 같은 <code>Array</code>에 있는 어떤 특수 메소드는 없습니다.</p>\n<p>이름으로 특정 속성에 접근하려면, <a href=\"ko/DOM/element.getAttribute\">getAttribute</a> 메소드를 쓰세요.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".eb.aa.85.ec.84.b8","title":"명세","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Core/core.html#ID-84CF096\" rel=\" noopener\">W3C DOM Level 2 Core: attributes</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-3-Core/core.html#ID-84CF096\" rel=\" noopener\">W3C DOM Level 3 Core: attributes</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-3-Core/core.html#ID-1780488922\" rel=\" noopener\">W3C DOM Level 3 NamedNodeMap interface</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"주어진 요소의 속성 모음(collection)을 반환합니다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Element.attributes","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Element.attributes","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"element.attributes","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Element.attributes","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"element.attributes","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Element.attributes","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Element.attributes","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Element.attributes","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Element.attributes","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/api/element/attributes","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/web/api/element/attributes/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web","title":"개발자를 위한 웹 기술"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API/Element","title":"Element"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API/Element/attributes","title":"element.attributes"}],"pageTitle":"element.attributes - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}